9... h6
{ played by Vitiugov against me. It can be just met with  10.h5  , passing the ball back, but the move I played was also good. }
10. b4 cxb3 11. Nxb3 Nxb3
{ And here I took on b3, and somehow won anyway, but much stronger would be to start by rerouting the knight. }
