7... e6 8. Be3
{ Keeping the options open. This is a funky alternative to natural development with Nf3 and O-O. }
8... Nge7 9. Rc1 { We can make a useful move before unleashing g4. } 9... Nc8
{ Is not a great way of developing here, as White gets to expand on the kingside. }
