cxd4 Ne7
{ The knight is usually heading to c6, but we can now set a small trap. } 12.
Rd1 { Waiting to see where the Black knight is heading towards. } 12... Nc6
{ Falling for it. If  12...Nf5  then just  13.Nf3  with a pleasant position for White, but nothing more than that. }
