{ This is certainly the toughest nut to crack and the most principled line one can play against the Advance variation. The fact that GM Erwin l'Ami chose this as the main weapon for his LTR Caro-Kann says enough! After meticulous research, though, I have come up with an excellent weapon for White - one that fits our repertoire conceptually, but is also challenging enough theoretically! }
