13. h4
{ I really like the creativity behind this idea. We want to gain a favorable structure on the kingside with h5 and if Black stops that, we get a great outpost for our bishop. }
13... h5 14. Bg5
{ The bishop on g5 is going to cause Black a lot of headaches. Meanwhile  14...cxd4  is always met with  15.Nxd4  . }
