{ I faced this setup once against Firouzja in a blitz game and failed to spot the right plan, which is Nfe1 f4. }
10. Nfe1 Be7 11. f4 O-O 12. Bd3
{ And White had an overwhelming advantage in Markgraf-Doettling, Bundesliga 2022. Next up is the f5 push and if need be, we can add Ne3 to the mix, to strengthen this push. }
