{ The computers obsesses over the queenside space in the Advanced Caro and here it does too. While it appears as though Black is intending to directly attack us on the kingside, the all-knowing engines decide it's a good moment to grab space! There is no rush or panic dealing with the g5-g4 push. }
7... g5
{ After  7...a5  we follow up with  8.Na3!  intending to relocate the knight to c2. }
8. a5 Nd7 9. c4
{ We are somewhat opening up the center, while Black is struggling to come up with further ideas on the kingside. }
