{ We could go  13.a4  ,  but we can also just let b5 happen- it could be a weakening. }
13... b5 14. a3 Qb8
{ Creative, but it doesn't change the nature of the position. } 15. Bh6 Qb6 16.
Bf1
{ Next we can choose our aggression level: do we want to play it slow, or go for some g4 business and do some brave kingside action? Both are valid options. }
