{ This was the choice of Naroditsky against Ray Robson in US Champs 2021. I also tried  16...Bh7  17.Qc1!  Kh8  18.Bg1  e5  , but White keeps some opening advantage after  both  19.dxe5  as well as  19.d5  . Also the immediate  17.c5!  looks strong:  17...Nd5  18.Bg1  intending Bb5 once again. }
